        &gt; <a class="colorMe" target="_blank" href="https://vimeo.com/196509630">dadageek::processing</a>, an introductory course to Processing and creative coding (2016) <br>
        &gt; <a class="colorMe" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/jromeem/ddgk-gltch">Glitch Art</a>, a Processing workshop on glitch art (2018) <br>
